Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.94,0:00:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時候 太陽化作仁慈的母親
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.10,0:00:13.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼓勵著地上的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.02,0:00:16.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時候又化作嚴厲的父親
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.35,0:00:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,予以考驗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.02,0:00:22.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,創世以來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.93,0:00:27.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經重複過多次的考驗 又將襲來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.50,0:00:35.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大地乾涸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.32,0:00:36.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海洋消失
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.59,0:00:39.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取而代之的是廣闊的沙海
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.48,0:00:43.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依靠稀薄的大氣層而倖存下來的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.34,0:00:46.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大多數生命體
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.26,0:00:51.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在 頻臨滅絕的危機
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.28,0:01:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 即使在看起來纖弱的生命中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.47,0:01:04.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有那麼一群堅強的人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.36,0:01:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們賭上微弱的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.95,0:01:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在無盡的沙海中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.20,0:01:11.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努力地活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.03,0:03:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,500)\pos(181,470)\fnSimSun\fs30}第一話 沙鯨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.78,0:03:10.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.83,0:03:35.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪雅大人 請別讓我太難做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.39,0:03:56.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼什麼什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.23,0:04:03.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Theseus的沙上驅逐艦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.40,0:04:06.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被追的是什麼人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.37,0:04:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿度亞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.87,0:04:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須快點去救人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.08,0:04:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前方多普勒效應 是相當大範圍的QTF
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.71,0:04:23.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.82,0:04:27.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本艦前方地下約100米
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.26,0:04:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,80 60
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.73,0:04:30.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OZMA
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.86,0:04:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道...難道...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.24,0:04:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OZMA確認
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.17,0:04:46.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左滿舵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.21,0:05:19.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.97,0:06:24.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那是OZMA 絕對是OZMA
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.31,0:06:26.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡可惡 可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.41,0:06:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是逮住它的好機會
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.55,0:06:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫薩姆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.89,0:06:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薩姆・寇因
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.22,0:06:40.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.70,0:06:54.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫瑪雅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.14,0:06:58.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...謝謝你救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.64,0:07:02.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這...這樣啊 你叫瑪雅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.82,0:07:08.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 你餓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.75,0:07:09.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.45,0:07:12.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃一頓好的 就有精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.85,0:07:13.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓緊了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.01,0:07:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(710,700)\fnSimSun\fs28\pos(320,475)}奧亞澤港
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.29,0:08:23.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.09,0:08:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.23,0:08:29.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.86,0:08:33.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意點啊 摔了可要被船長臭罵一頓了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.94,0:08:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 薩姆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.04,0:08:37.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.61,0:08:40.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薩姆？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.48,0:08:44.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.62,0:08:51.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.99,0:08:59.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 這裡是我們船上的食堂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.00,0:09:02.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 果然已經擠滿人了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.86,0:09:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的師傅 手藝可是奧亞澤一絕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.74,0:09:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 對不住你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.71,0:09:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 坐這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.74,0:09:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔 午飯兩份
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.38,0:09:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 特製套餐2份
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.91,0:09:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.02,0:09:23.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薩姆 薩姆 薩姆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.42,0:09:25.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來一下來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.05,0:09:27.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事啊 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.79,0:09:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪撿回個這麼個大美人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.13,0:09:36.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 這說起來話就長了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.07,0:09:45.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誘拐啊 幹得好 給你加兩個捷蜥蜴的蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.04,0:09:49.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人做事就該當機立斷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.75,0:09:56.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了不是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.30,0:10:12.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 別擠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.53,0:10:13.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.70,0:10:15.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.74,0:10:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.11,0:10:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓開啊 這樣叫人怎麼進去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.51,0:10:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.31,0:10:26.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 我 讓 開
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.61,0:10:27.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.49,0:10:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.20,0:10:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.87,0:10:47.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊 薩姆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.77,0:10:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米梅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.04,0:10:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟船長報告了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.27,0:10:55.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 還沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.48,0:11:04.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這可不行 都受傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.75,0:11:06.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須接受治療
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.07,0:11:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.37,0:11:22.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.04,0:11:26.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷已經不礙事了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.48,0:11:31.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要來一杯嗎 提神良藥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.78,0:11:33.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大夫你真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.41,0:11:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.59,0:11:44.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷 真夠勁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.83,0:11:46.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 大夫你真是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.06,0:12:00.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真差勁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.87,0:12:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本以為你是去找沙鯨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.98,0:12:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然撿了個女人回來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.90,0:12:06.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.71,0:12:08.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼個不對法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.85,0:12:11.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她被Theseus的沙上驅逐艦追捕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.89,0:12:15.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後連OZMA...沙鯨都出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.36,0:12:16.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.57,0:12:19.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥常說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.44,0:12:22.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為男人 要幫助弱小者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.95,0:12:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我作為男人 怎麼能見死不救
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.70,0:12:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟是個美人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.86,0:12:31.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.43,0:12:33.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 船長
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.11,0:12:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個叫瑪雅的 好像有什麼隱情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.29,0:12:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能讓她留下來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.49,0:12:43.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瘟神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.57,0:12:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這...這說得太過了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.99,0:12:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.35,0:12:57.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.50,0:12:59.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？什麼？我沒聽到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.59,0:13:03.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船長
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.13,0:13:07.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船長 是Theseus
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.26,0:13:10.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍隊那些傢夥 似乎打算登陸這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.39,0:13:14.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 早就顯示在卡片上了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.13,0:13:28.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.06,0:13:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍隊的船嗎 為什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.63,0:13:52.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.00,0:14:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡不是你們該來的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.57,0:14:13.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 趕快滾回去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.41,0:14:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舉槍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.52,0:14:31.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢夥 到底有何目的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.59,0:14:34.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道 是來追那個女人的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.70,0:14:35.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.79,0:14:38.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍隊追到這裡來 說明...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.59,0:14:41.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薩姆 那個女人是什麼來頭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.11,0:14:43.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你問我 我也不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.35,0:14:48.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又給我惹麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.14,0:14:50.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.57,0:14:53.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船長
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.37,0:15:05.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是興師動眾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.89,0:15:11.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是船長嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.10,0:15:17.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們收到消息 說我們追捕的人上了你們的船
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.02,0:15:21.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道 有這回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.47,0:15:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把舷梯放下來 這是軍隊的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.85,0:15:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.94,0:15:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.02,0:15:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為會弄髒我的船的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.93,0:15:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢夥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.75,0:15:35.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獨立獨行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.90,0:15:37.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不阿諛奉承
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.83,0:15:40.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝著船頭前進的方向活下去 是我們的主張
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.36,0:15:44.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備射擊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.98,0:16:11.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪雅大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.33,0:16:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把槍放下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.71,0:16:19.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在就過去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.62,0:16:30.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 願意這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.73,0:16:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給您添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.29,0:16:37.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是令人羨慕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.11,0:16:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有著一群出色的夥伴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.94,0:16:48.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 說的挺煽情的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.11,0:16:50.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薩姆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.57,0:16:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.49,0:16:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米梅 瑪雅就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.07,0:16:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.97,0:17:01.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快 從這裡下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.35,0:17:05.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪雅 快 進船去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.65,0:17:09.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.50,0:17:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船長 你的壞毛病又發作了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.99,0:17:15.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 天性嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.61,0:17:19.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小的們 起航了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.48,0:17:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 船長
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.23,0:17:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開工了 小的們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.14,0:18:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楞著幹什麼 給我射
